Some Beijing Banks End Mortgage Discounts, Securities Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-02-23T23:25:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-23/five-beijing-banks-end-mortgage-discounts-china-securities-journal-says.html
Five banks in Beijing stopped giving
discounts on the benchmark interest rate for mortage loans to
buy first homes, the China Securities Journal reported today,
citing unidentified bank officials.  The banks include Industrial and Commercial Bank of China
Ltd.,  Agricultural Bank of China Ltd .,  Bank of China Ltd .,  China
Construction Bank Corp . and Bank of Communications Co., the
report said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 jliu42@bloomberg.net  